//simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/28/pip-261/#atom-everything", "source": "Simon Willison's Blog", "date": "2026-04-28", "summary": "What&#x27;s new in pip 26.1 - lockfiles and dependency cooldowns!\nRichard Si describes an excellent set of upgrades to Python's default pip tool for installing dependencies.\nThis version drops support"}, {"title": "russellromney/honker", "url": "https://simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/24/honker/#atom-everything", "source": "Simon Willison's Blog", "date": "2026-04-24", "summary": "russellromney/honker\n\"Postgres NOTIFY/LISTEN semantics\" for SQLite, implemented as a Rust SQLite extension and various language bindings to help make use of it.\nThe design of this looks very solid. It"}, {"title": "Serving the For You feed", "url": "https://simonwillison.net/2026/Apr/24/serving-the-for-you-feed/#atom-everything", "source": "Simon Willison's Blog", "date": "2026-04-24", "summary": "Serving the For You feed\nOne of Bluesky's most interesting features is that anyone can run their own custom \"feed\" implementation and make it available to other users - effectively enabling custom alg"}]}], "highlights": [{"icon": "🧠", "name": "大模型与基础架构", "color": "#7c3aed", "count": 75, "text": "大模型军备竞赛进入新阶段。Google 的 Gemma 系列持续开源，强化在移动端和边缘设备上的部署能力；Anthropic 的 Claude 系列以安全性和长文本理解见长，在企业级市场获得认可；OpenAI 的 GPT 系列维持技术领先但面临日益激烈的竞争。小型化高效模型（sub-10B）异军突起，在消费级 GPU 上即可达到接近旗舰模型的性能。"}, {"icon": "🤯", "name": "AI Agent与智能体", "color": "#d97706", "count": 18, "text": "AI Agent 正从实验走向生产级部署。MCP 和 A2A 两大协议标准的推进，正在为智能体互操作性铺平道路。在软件开发领域，以 OpenHands、Cursor 和 Claude Code 为代表的 AI Coding Agent 已经嵌入真实开发流程，从辅助工具升级为核心生产力。百度 GenFlow 4.0 更将 Agent 能力扩展到 Office 三件套。"}, {"icon": "🤖", "name": "具身智能与机器人", "color": "#059669", "count": 6, "text": "具身智能的技术栈正在快速收敛。感知层面多模态融合成为标配，决策层面基于大模型的技能学习替代传统强化学习，执行层面灵巧手和力矩传感的成熟使精细操作成为可能。政策层面，中国「十四五」规划将具身智能列为重点发展方向。"}, {"icon": "🎨", "name": "多模态与AIGC", "color": "#dc2626", "count": 16, "text": "统一架构革命正在改变多模态 AI 的游戏规则。新一代 VLM 正在将图像理解与图像生成合二为一。视频生成领域，Sora 的突破性进展推动了大量替代方案涌现。音频侧，AudioLDM 2 在推理速度上实现突破，消费级 GPU 即可实时完成语音合成和音乐生成。"}, {"icon": "💾", "name": "AI硬件与芯片", "color": "#0891b2", "count": 9, "text": "AI 芯片竞争从云端延伸到端侧。NVIDIA 凭借 CUDA 生态持续主导训练市场，但推理侧格局正在变化——Groq 的 LPU 架构在推理速度上实现突破，AMD 的 ROCm 生态加速追赶。端侧 AI 部署成为最热新趋势，7B 级别模型可以在手机上跑推理。"}], "trending": {"cards": [{"full_name": "warpdotdev/warp", "url": "https://github.com/warpdotdev/warp", "stars": 41110, "stars_today": 11955, "description": "Warp is an agentic development environment, born out of the terminal.", "language": "Rust", "ai_score": 70}, {"full_name": "sponsors/mattpocock", "url": "https://github.com/sponsors/mattpocock", "stars": 42354, "stars_today": 7356, "description": "Skills for Real Engineers. Straight from my .claude directory.", "language": "Shell", "ai_score": 55}, {"full_name": "microsoft/VibeVoice", "url": "https://github.com/microsoft/VibeVoice", "stars": 45491, "stars_today": 1688, "description": "Open-Source Frontier Voice AI", "language": "Python", "ai_score": 45}, {"full_name": "sponsors/obra", "url": "https://github.com/sponsors/obra", "stars": 172731, "stars_today": 1683, "description": "An agentic skills framework &amp; software development methodology that works.", "language": "Shell", "ai_score": 55}, {"full_name": "ComposioHQ/awesome-codex-skills", "url": "https://github.com/ComposioHQ/awesome-codex-skills", "stars": 4594, "stars_today": 1180, "description": "A curated list of practical Codex skills for automating workflows across the Codex CLI and API.", "language": "Python", "ai_score": 35}, {"full_name": "sponsors/abhigyanpatwari", "url": "https://github.com/sponsors/abhigyanpatwari", "stars": 33150, "stars_today": 777, "description": "GitNexus: The Zero-Server Code Intelligence Engine - GitNexus is a client-side knowledge graph creator that runs entirely in your browser. Drop in a G", "language": "TypeScript", "ai_score": 55}, {"full_name": "sponsors/EbookFoundation", "url": "https://github.com/sponsors/EbookFoundation", "stars": 387021, "stars_today": 609,